<br>
  <br>
<br>
1)      listener’s reactions; <br>
<br>
2)      listener’s apprehension of harm; <br>
<br>
3)      speaker’s intent; <br>
<br>
4)      conditional nature of the statements; and <br>
<br>
5)      attendant circumstances. <br>
